cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an online learning algorithm that improves regret guarantees for ill-conditioned data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories. The use of sketching techniques and sparse forms of sketching methods suggest that the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
